sonal style is a concern, it is the only documented weakness and could be mitigated through training or crew pairing. The other candidates either lack critical reliability or stress\u2011handling data, or have stronger documented teamwork/communication issues without compensating strengths.\n**Therefore, I support selecting Candidate\u202fB** for the long\u2011distance pilot position.\nMETADATA_JSON:\n{\"agent\": \"agent_3\", \"vote\": \"Candidate B\"}"}
